cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the problem of finding good camera poses for a robot to gain semantic knowledge about an observed object. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper deals with object recognition and image understanding. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a solution using a neural network to predict a "semantic score". 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a solution using deep learning techniques. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with understanding the semantic meaning of objects from different views.
